## System Architecture

Raw Wearable Signals (EDA / HRV)
            |
            v
   Signal Preprocessing
 (Detrending, Normalization)
            |
            v
   Sliding Window Segmentation
        (256 samples)
            |
            v
 High-Dimensional Feature Space
      (Physiological States)
            |
            v
   Dimensionality Reduction
          (PCA Lens)
            |
            v
   Topological Covering
      (Hypercubes)
            |
            v
   Local Clustering
        (DBSCAN)
            |
            v
  Topological Stress Graph
 (States + Transitions)
            |
            v
 Interactive Visualization
   (stress_topology.html)
